metadata.description:
I created "Breathe" out of simply being tired. 

Being a twin dad while pursuing a career as a DIY artist can be stressful, and at times feel hopeless.

By creating "Breathe", i was able to in a sense "breathe again" through being vulnerable + remembering that it will all come in time.

Written, Recorded + Mixed by Nessy the Rilla
Produced by Noane
Recorded At The Pharmacy Studios - Houston, TX
